Name
       editDeleteFillet  - Deletes the tear-drop fillet that was added between
       a wire and bump connection with the editAddFillet command

Syntax
       editDeleteFillet [-help]

       Deletes the tear-drop fillet that was added between  a  wire  and  bump
       connection with the editAddFillet command.

Parameters
       -help  Prints  the  usage of the command. For a detailed description of
              the command, use the man command:

              man editDeleteFillet

